# SAENA foundation

## Purpose

Enforce product principles during any Cursor edit.

## Scope

Entire repository.

## Current decision

CONFIRMED principles from design specs.

## Principles (must reflect in structure/docs)

1. API-first
2. contract-first
3. event-contract-first
4. tenant-aware (`tenant_id`, `workspace_id`, `project_id`, `site_id`, `run_id`, `actor_id`)
5. evidence-first
6. human-approval-gated
7. deployment-profile separation
8. algorithm/infrastructure separation
9. provider adapter separation
10. least privilege
11. immutable audit trail
12. observable-by-default
13. test-first
14. no deployment by execution agents
15. customer source isolation

## Engine (v1)

- ChatGPT Search only
- Google AI Overviews / AI Mode / Gemini: OUT OF SCOPE for optimize/observe/claim

## Constraints

- Do not invent specs not in `docs/specs/`
- Do not implement AEO algorithms, APIs, crawlers, Temporal, live Helm in bootstrap follow-ups without Plan
- Never commit secrets

## Status

CONFIRMED
